  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Minotaur Limb Replacement",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "弥诺陶洛斯肢体替换组件",
    "TraditionalChinese": "彌諾陶洛斯四肢替換零件"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A collection of salvaged components from a Sentinel Hardframe, reconditioned to fit the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid.<br><br>This limb override also functions as its own <span class=\"name name-stellar\">dedicated combat system</span>. It deploys high-velocity <span class=\"name name-technology\">stun projectiles</span> and serves as an excellent support weapon to the Minotaur's primary cannon.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to cycle available weapon modes.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一组从护卫强化外壳上回收的构件，经过改造后适用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇。<br><br>这个肢体超控自身也可以作为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">专用战斗系统</span>。它可以部署高速<span class=\"name name-technology\">眩晕弹</span>，是弥诺陶洛斯主炮的绝佳辅助武器。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CLEWEAPON</span>以循环可用的武器模式。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從巡警硬體結構中回收的一系列元件，經過翻新後用於<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇。<br><br>此肢體覆寫能夠充當<span class=\"name name-stellar\">專用戰鬥系統</span>。會部署高速的<span class=\"name name-technology\">暈眩射彈</span>，是彌諾陶洛斯主砲的絕佳輔助武器。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 切換可用武器模式。"
  },
